<p>Saturday 16/6/17<br/>Two years since leaving Sydney. Marched to Varennes and proceeded by train to Bapaume &ndash; relieving 8th Bde.<br/>Sunday 17/6/17<br/>Church Parade. Wrote to Doff. Played 28th cricket &amp; won &ndash; I made 48 top score.<br/>Monday 18/6/17<br/>Training as usual. Bas had dinner with me &ndash; rode home with him &amp; saw Martin.<br/>Tuesday 19/6/17<br/>Training &amp; preparation for Field Day tomorrow, raining slightly, letters from Doff.</p>
